Author: thefakemexoxo
Text: I’ve always known that I’d be fucked in a zombie apocalypse. I have a bad immune system, I’m easily injured, Im not very strong, I’m a woman (I’m gonna get raped), and I have bad eyesight. About the only thing I used to have was endurance running. If the zombie apocalypse hits, I’ll personally take my own way out 😅

Author: attenuatingpixie333
Text: Sometimes when I'm restricting and exercising, I'm like "I'm not disordered, I'm just preparing! When the zombie apocalypse happens, I'll be so ready!" When in reality, I'll just be even more fucked because I'll probably be lacking in lots of nutrients from the starts 😂🤦🏼‍♀️
